title: Haunted House on Sorority Row (2014)
description:
Haunted House on Sorority Row (2014)

Director: Henrique Couto

Writer: John Oak Dalton

Stars: Haley Madison, Erin R. Ryan, Iabou Windimere 

Storyline

A fledging sorority moves into a dilapidated house only to find something evil is lurking in the shadows. Is it an elaborate hazing ritual? Or is something sinister - something paranormal - behind the mental and physical assault?

Plot Keywords: vomiting | supernatural power | ghost | starvation | self confidence 

Taglines: Something in this house is effecting these girls' minds... and bodies... 

Genres: Horror 

Country: USA
Runtime: 81 min 

Language: English

Release Date: 21 February 2014 (USA)
